ble\r\n	{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\n	mso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\n	mso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\n	mso-style-noshow:yes;\r\n	mso-style-parent:\"\";\r\n	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\n	mso-para-margin:0cm;\r\n	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\n	mso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\n	font-size:10.0pt;\r\n	font-family:\"\'Times New Roman\'\";\r\n	mso-fareast-font-family:\"\'Times New Roman\'\";\r\n	mso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\n	mso-bidi-language:#0400;}</style>\r\n<p><!--StartFragment--><span style=\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-family: \'宋体\'\">◆</span><!--EndFragment--> 轻便型的头带结构坚固耐用，自动调节设计适用于不同人体头型佩带，质量轻，佩带舒适，真正满足长时间音乐工作者使用；</p>\r\n<p><!--StartFragment--><span style=\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-family: \'宋体\'\">◆</span><!--EndFragment--> 封闭式声腔结构设计，超大柔软的皮革耳垫佩戴舒适，可以完全罩住耳朵，有效隔绝环境噪声，在噪杂环境中也不影响监听效果；</p>\r\n<p><!--StartFragment--><span style=\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-family: \'宋体\'\">◆</span><!--EndFragment--> 53mm超大振膜驱动单元，低频真实饱满，中频精确，高频清澈透明，宽广的动态范围，无论是在监听、混音或者是欣赏音乐你都能享受到精准而细腻的音色；</p>\r\n<p><!--StartFragment--><span style=\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: ZH-CN; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-bidi-font-family: \'宋体\'\">◆</span><!--EndFragment--> 信号线采用单边出线设计，99.99%OFC无氧铜屏蔽线，音频信号传输快，噪音低，螺纹式插头，可避免接触不良及有噪音等不良现象。</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin-top: 10px\">适用范围：</h4>\r\n适用于录音室监听、电脑/数位录音监听、电脑游戏、欣赏音乐等专业场所。\r\n<h4 style=\"margin-top: 10px\">技术参数：</h4>\r\n<p>耳机类型：封闭式耳机</p>\r\n<p>驱动单元：53mm</p>\r\n<p>阻抗：60欧</p>\r\n<p>灵敏度；94&plusmn;3dB</p>\r\n<p>频率响应：10-30kHz</p>\r\n<p>最大功率：1200mW</p>\r\n<p>信号线长：约3米</p>\r\n<p>接驳插头：立体声3.5+6.3螺旋转换插头</p>\r\n<p>重量：280克（含信号线）</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin-top: 10px\">标准配置：</h4>\r\n1、HP-680耳机 1PC 2、6.3镀金螺纹转换插头 1PC 3、说明书+合格证+保修卡 1份 4、彩盒+内架包装</div>','images/201304/thumb_img/1472_thumb_G_1366920098200.jpg','images/201304/goods_img/1472_G_1366920098788.jpg','images/201304/source_img/1472_G_1366920098041.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1366920098','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1367261492','0','','-1','-1','0','0');
