约250克（不含信号线）</p>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin-top: 10px\">标准配置：</h4>\r\n1、HP-980耳机 1PC 2、信号线 1PC 3、6.3镀金螺纹转换插头 1PC 4、说明书+合格证+保修卡 1份 5、彩盒+珍珠棉包装</div>','images/201304/thumb_img/1473_thumb_G_1366920227077.jpg','images/201304/goods_img/1473_G_1366920227681.jpg','images/201304/source_img/1473_G_1366920227514.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1366920227','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1367261490','0','','-1','-1','0','0');
INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('1474','92','DT001474','ISK-AT2000','+','82','0','','100','0.000','115.00','115.00','110.00','0','0','1','','','<div class=\"proingshow\">\r\n<div id=\"show\"><a href=\"http://www.nbisk.cn/uploadfile/products/big/PN-2011919125836_0.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[plants]\"><img id=\"bidimg\" src=\"http://www.nbisk.cn/uploadfile/products/big/PN-2011919125836_0.jpg\" width=\"400\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"picDemo\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; width: 440px; overflow: hidden\"><a href=\"http://www.nbisk.cn/uploadfile/products/big/PN-2011919125836_1.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[plants]\"><img id=\"sidimg\" class=\"shadowbox floatL\" src=\"http://www.nbisk.cn/uploadfile/products/big/PN-2011919125836_1.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" rel=\"lightbox[roadtrip]\" style=\"margin: 3px; cursor: pointer\" alt=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.nbisk.cn/uploadfile/products/big/PN-2011919125836_2.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[plants]\"><img id=\"sidimg\" class=\"shadowbox floatL\" src=\"http://www.nbisk.cn/uploadfile/products/big/PN-2011919125836_2.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" rel=\"lightbox[roadtrip]\" style=\"margin: 3px; cursor: pointer\" alt=\"\" /></a><a href=\"http://www.nbisk.cn/uploadfile/products/big/PN-2011919125836_3.jpg\" rel=\"lightbox[plants]\"><img id=\"sidimg\" class=\"shadowbox floatL\" src=\"http://www.nbisk.cn/uploadfile/products/big/PN-2011919125836_3.jpg\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" rel=\"lightbox[roadtrip]\" style=\"margin: 3px; cursor: pointer\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"proSm\">\r\n<h4>产品特性：</h4>\r\n<p><!--StartFragment--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span>AT2000是最新研发的一款轻便型全封闭式监听耳机，封闭性好、体积小、质量轻、佩戴舒适，配置最新40mm钕磁驱动单元，具有精准纯净的音质，舒适的耳垫，即使长时间佩戴也倍感轻松。适用于欣赏音乐、钢琴乐器看电影及各种监听场所。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><font style=\"font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5pt\"><span style=\"mso-ascii-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-hansi-font-fa