bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n佩戴方式：头戴压耳式</div>\r\n<div>换能方式：动圈式喇叭</div>\r\n<div>驱动单元：￠40mm</div>\r\n<div>阻抗：32&Omega;</div>\r\n<div>灵敏度：95&plusmn;3dB</div>\r\n<div>频率响应：15Hz-20kHz</div>\r\n<div>最大功率:400mW&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>额定功率：250&nbsp;mW</div>\r\n<div>线长：约3m（直线）</div>\r\n<div>插头：￠3.5mm+￠6.3mm</div>\r\n<div>净量：233克（含线）</div>\r\n<div>接触压力：2.8N<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h4 style=\"margin-top: 10px\">标准配置：</h4>\r\nAT2000耳机：1个<br />\r\n6.3转换插头：1个<br />\r\n产品说明书+合格证+保修卡：各一份<br />\r\n彩盒+内架：1个</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','images/201304/thumb_img/1474_thumb_G_1366920462539.jpg','images/201304/goods_img/1474_G_1366920462685.jpg','images/201304/source_img/1474_G_1366920462081.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1366920462','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1367261487','0','','-1','-1','0','0');
