div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork_bt\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_bt_it\"><span>产品功能</span><span class=\"s2\">Product Function</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"formwork\">\r\n<div class=\"formwork_text\">\r\n<div class=\"proshow0107_1\"><img class=\"err-product\" alt=\"\" style=\"float: left\" src=\"http://img20.360buyimg.com/vc/g7/M01/12/04/rBEHZVDqiWAIAAAAAAAYhA0kY24AADi1QP5BLYAABic016.gif\" />\r\n<h3>40纳米新制程技术</h3>\r\n<p>AMD HD5000系列采用40纳米新制程技术，不仅使晶圆面积缩小，更因电子线路间的距离变小，让时脉速度可以大幅提升更为节能，并且可支援未来更新规格的高速记忆体，再创3D图形处理效能的</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','images/201304/thumb_img/1546_thumb_G_1367182887145.jpg','images/201304/goods_img/1546_G_1367182887211.jpg','images/201304/source_img/1546_G_1367182887002.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1367182887','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1377751081','5','','0','0','0','0');
