INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('1555','72','DT001555','漫步者R18T','+','71','0','','999','0.000','0.00','91.00','0.00','0','0','1','漫步者R18T 漫步者 R18T 电脑音箱','','<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">漫步者R18是一款经典的入门级立体声音箱产品，上市以来，凭借简洁的操控与出色的性价比备受市场认可，随后漫步者还推出了R18USB版本，均受到消费者广泛赞誉。当然，漫步者的更新步伐并未停止，全新的R18T也在近期正式上市，木质箱体，小巧体积，典雅造型，不俗音质，非常适合对外观有要求，又不希望占用过多桌面空间的用户。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r18tzl/1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">漫步者R18T音箱依然延续传统2.0声道箱体结构，对箱设计，采用细致的黑色木纹装潢，质感良好，造型更加出色。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r18tzl/2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">R18T的前面板使用了高穿透性的纱网面罩，底部采用银色塑料面板，铸模精确，相较R18，在保持体积小巧的同时，整体外观线条更加流畅，端庄的造型，又让R18T能协调融入桌面环境。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r18tzl/3.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">R18T的箱体沿用了全木质结构设计，用料充足，能够有效降低箱体谐振和箱声，为音箱良好发声打下良好基础。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r18tzl/4.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">R18T每声道均采用一只50&times;90mm的跑道型扬声器单元，全封闭的箱体设计，非常容易推动，声场开阔，完全足够满足日常听音需求。而且R18T还自带EMC屏蔽磁环，避免高频电磁干扰，摆放空间随心所欲。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r18tzl/5.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">为了让操控更加简洁，R18T所有的操作选项均被设计到了主箱的前面板位置，从左至右一次设置有耳机插孔、音量调节旋钮、电源指示灯、电源开关。R18T的音调电位器的旋转居中于箱体下方，较R18体积有所增加，手感平滑，阻尼良好，操控更准确，而且炫丽银也为箱体增色不少。考虑到许多用户使用耳机的习惯，R18T也加入了耳机输出，在连接耳机的时候，音箱会自动静音，而且音箱的音量控制自动变化为耳机音量控制，尽显人性化操控设计。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r18tzl/6.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">即使在脚垫这一细节，漫步者也毫不马虎，全部采用化学性质稳定的深灰色橡胶，摆放桌面更加稳固，同时既不容易被污染，也不污染家具。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r18tzl/7.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">如果早已厌倦了传统2.0声道音箱的大体积，想要寻找一款身形小巧同时能发出好声音的音箱，R18T将是一个不错的选择。出色的造型工艺，严谨的声学结构，简便的操控性以及出色的性价比，不仅不会为您造成购买上的负担，同时还将带来声色俱备的影音娱乐享受。</p>','images/201304/thumb_img/1555_thumb_G_1367186684205.jpg','images/201304/goods_img/1555_G_1367186684744.jpg','images/201304/source_img/1555_G_1367186684374.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1367186684','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1373109686','68','','0','0','0','0');
