INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('1558','72','DT001558','漫步者R600USB','+','63','0','','998','0.000','0.00','133.00','0.00','0','0','1','漫步者R600USB 漫步者 R600USB 电脑音箱','','<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r600usb1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">漫步者R600除了TC版之外还有一个USB版本，这一点在同级别音箱中并不多见，即使是畅销十余年的R1000TC北美版也没有USB版，足见漫步者对于R600系列的重视。与传统微箱相比，R600USB箱体更大，单元尺寸以及分频设计更加完美，能为笔记本用户提供更加出色的音质表现。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r600usb2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">外观上，R600USB与R600TC基本相同，木质箱体设计，采用低毒环保材料，杜绝污染，黑色木纹贴皮使得整体设计格调沉稳、大气，高音部分则采用了金属外观的挡板，在沉稳中透出一股锐气。箱体尺寸为140（宽）&times;226（高）&times;196（深）mm ，放在桌面上并不突兀，大小较为合适。音箱采用两分频设计，4英寸凹盆低中频扬声器，配合丝膜高音扬声器，音质柔美醇厚。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r600usb3.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">与R600TC不同，R600USB舍去外接电源的设计，采用单一USB插头，无需另外供电，进一步简化了操作，连线更方便，桌面也更加整洁，同时还增强了安全性。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r600usb4.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">此外，R600USB版使用USB数字音频解码电路，可直接接收数字音频信号，替代电脑板载声卡，自带的EMC屏蔽磁环，摆脱主板高频干扰，音质表现更加纯净。而高效率D类放大器的采用使得USB接口有限的电源供应下依然有强劲声音表现。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r600usb5.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">R600USB与R600TC观感上最大不同在于USB版多出一个线控调节器，一方面使得箱体更加简洁，另外双静音按键，搭配工作状态指示灯和数字音量控制，体现人性化操作设计，大大方便了日常应用。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/r600usb6.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">R600USB箱体连线十分简洁，无需繁琐连接，简单接线就能轻松享受音乐带来的乐趣。您只需将R600USB按主副箱顺序置于笔记本两侧，随手调节线控器即可实现全部听音操作。</p>','images/201304/thumb_img/1558_thumb_G_1367187003435.jpg','images/201304/goods_img/1558_G_1367187003067.jpg','images/201304/source_img/1558_G_1367187003648.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1367187003','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1373109814','68','','0','0','0','0');
