INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('1692','72','DT001692','漫步者S2.1M','+','92','0','','999','0.000','0.00','694.00','0.00','0','0','1','','','<p style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; text-transform: none; color: rgb(102,102,102); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">漫步者S级产品，饱含音乐的英雄主义，有追求的人士，胸中自有万马奔腾。只有S级产品能够释放满腔的激情。漫步者与您一样，激情永不熄灭。长久的期盼，执着的呼唤，漫步者NEW S系列，带着咝咝作响的炉温，烫伤你的眼球。重机械部队集结完毕，圣迹大战一触即发。</p>\r\n<p style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; text-transform: none; color: rgb(102,102,102); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong>Peter Duminy 简介：</strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; text-transform: none; color: rgb(102,102,102); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"1\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/scn2005/product/speaker/r1900tii06/11.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; text-transform: none; color: rgb(102,102,102); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">爱德发北美公司设计师---Peter Duminy</p>\r\n<p style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; text-transform: none; color: rgb(102,102,102); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: justify; widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">拥有30年音响设计经验，曾就职于于B.B.C（英国广播公司）扬声器研发部，Bowers &amp; Wilkins Loudspeakers Ltd (B&amp;W), 和 Monsoon Audio. 他于2004年加入加拿大爱德发的研发团队。无论是在高保真，还是多媒体行业，Peter始终工作于研发的前沿。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"word-spacing: 