INSERT INTO necs_goods VALUES('1610','72','DT001610','漫步者E2200','+','58','0','','999','0.000','0.00','304.00','0.00','0','0','1','漫步者E2200 漫步者 E2200 电脑音箱','','<div style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 24px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); margin-left: 185px; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><strong>E2200详细资料</strong></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">自推出e3100以来，时尚、音质、性价比就成为漫步者e系列产品的标志，2.1声道多媒体音箱也由此进入音质与外观并重的时代。当然，漫步者前进的步伐并未停止，全新上市的e2200进一步壮大e系列，更前卫的造型，更出众的音质，e2200与早些时候推出的e2100形成姊妹搭配，共同组成了多媒体音箱市场上一道亮丽的风景线。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e2200zl/1.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">漫步者e2200采用了大胆的黑白色调设计。全木质低音箱体能有效杜绝谐振和箱声，由于外壳部分采用白色PU漆与黑色磨砂工艺装饰，给人一种镜面般的光泽感，整体造型透露出一种玲珑细致的高雅情调。黑白相接处的完美线条设计以及动感的三角型调节钮，令e2200体现出新潮的居家风格。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e2200zl/2.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">不同于e2100，e2200的低音箱体采用了传统的立式箱体设计，倒相孔放置于箱体侧后方，专利双曲面倒相孔设计大大降低风噪，也提升了整体解析力。而5英寸低音单元也带来强劲低频表现。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e2200zl/3.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">在低音箱前面板设置有音量旋钮、高音增益旋钮和低音增益旋钮，三个控制旋钮都被设计成三角柱体，时尚而且防滑，方便用户对声音进行精细调节，而且不需要挪动音箱即可实现，充分彰显漫步者产品对于细节的关注。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e2200zl/4.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">由于控制按钮前置，低音箱体背面的布局十分简单，音频输入和输出接口通过颜色的区分连接简单。此外，e2200还采用功放电路低噪声设计，内置运放之皇NE5532确保前极信号高质驱动，使低音更为结实有力，电解电容更是采用两颗4700微法容量，有效改善音质。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e2200zl/5.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">e2200的卫星箱采用了漫步者自主研发的3英寸中高音扬声器单元，时尚的灰色泡边，精致的白纤维纸振膜，音质纯正耐听。全防磁设计使得摆放不受限制。与e2100相同，e2200的扬声器单元并没有设计单独的网罩，而是搭配可拆卸的透明有机玻璃面板，使卫星箱看起来更加时尚清秀。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e2200zl/6.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">e2200的底座也非常有特点，亚光铝制椭圆型金属底座，中间翘起托起整个音箱，使扬声器形成一定角度的上扬，减少了声波和桌面的漫反射，将音质损失降到最低。由于金属托架在某些表面（如玻璃等）放置或者移动时会发出一种刺耳的摩擦声，因此托架底部的四个角分别装有橡胶皮垫，防止打滑和发出噪音。</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.edifier.com/sce2009/product/speaker/e2200zl/7.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; widows: 2; text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; font: 12px/20px Tahoma; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(102,102,102); word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">时尚新颖的外观设计，出众造型工艺，5英寸低音单元配合３英寸中高音单元带来纯正音质表现，漫步者e2200，形色兼备，表里皆有，绝对是家居办公时尚之选。</p>','images/201304/thumb_img/1610_thumb_G_1367197262550.jpg','images/201304/goods_img/1610_G_1367197262460.jpg','images/201304/source_img/1610_G_1367197262644.jpg','1','','1','1','0','0','1367197262','100','0','0','0','0','0','0','1373113154','68','','0','0','0','0');
